{"tid":1866340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係笑柒班醫護 佢地信連登班暖氣軍師已經自取滅亡 黎明行動同開花 罷工 班仆街連登仔有邊穫唔係得個講字","createTime":"2020-02-06T16:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T05:48:11.000Z","uid":252492,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"347d3aa83d02feeece748b409a6b188451513712","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:49:43.000Z","msg":"黎明水鳩左班學生妹出黎比藍絲拖入車箱毒打<br />\n班仆街連登仔同一時間係時事台開侵侵直播post打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c70983bd3c447ef1c935325decfadbf13936a4f","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:51:13.000Z","msg":"根本連登仔就係無出黎罷工班醫護會員<br />\n只係煽風點火但又唔會出黎 剩係想坐享享其成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49de5b73bfe4ab3967bda2fb7745ef786d7f3e3","tid":1866340,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"[香港人，反抗] 要贏，必須升級至 全民三罷，甚至 全民勇武<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1866282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1866282</a><br />\n<br />\n無論係 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武</span></strong></span> 或者 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罷緊工</span></span></strong> 既手足 都捱唔到好耐<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「我地以為一二一二係衝，點知人地一二一二係退既。」<br />\n<br />\n「望返後面已經冇晒人。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果佢話三罷，或者罷鐵、罷藍舖頭，講完你要真係做先得架。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n擺在面前有兩套方法，<br />\n其一是  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全民有心理準備作正面衝突</span>，<br />\n其二是  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全民落實罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n「但係好多人就係覺得，去到呢個樽頸唔知點做。其實佢心入面明明就知呢兩樣野。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「希望大家唔好淨係識得講香港人反抗，反抗係做出嚟架，唔係你鳩噏架！」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我地個個都有夢想架，我地個個都有啲野想做，但係，我地肯犧牲嗰啲野嚟上前線爭取啊！」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n勇武 同 醫護 都唔係condom，<br />\n所有珍惜生命既香港人，<br />\n以及願意付出更多既抗爭者，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">請你地加入呢次罷工！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n對於全民勇武已經唔抱太大既希望，但係呢次武漢肺炎係一個發動罷工既大好機會<br />\n希望全香港人可以真正團結一次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzoa9L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzoa9L.png&h=f8666165&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2da3f3100a92f7e6820c682e4570955f87db0813","tid":1866340,"uid":20690,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:02:46.000Z","msg":"真，最後要返大陸做醫護唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40967c669c19305bb31e168240c8e6084d8cc65e","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd5c90d79767bb7ae3125ea65e638f3190da6a3","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c592a4560b4474fb1223d520ed64f1edd3101b7f","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412af692cba1e8daadcb2ae0a9713f7cf2744e7a","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:24:37.000Z","msg":"玻璃心連登仔不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc1dc0d7569abec7f6ab0c64defe8e144b5da72","tid":1866340,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:28:40.000Z","msg":"唔通出嚟行動嘅就一定唔係連登仔？念力睇post？<br />\n五毛post想抹黑勇武，收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981037aec05dd0845e28eb01140559ce3799b9fa","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f83a9611c931efe0dddc1f0f37ca5a5db265245","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b8694c36c0444035ac2f55d08527a9dd083932","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T19:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e6749da15a9bbcac9c9ed0d3eaecc4f48274c6","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T21:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43c9795a79239857e3da4794cb22f983228e869","tid":1866340,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:23:08.000Z","msg":"五味冰火依隻<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛狗</span></span>又出嚟做野<br />\n<br />\n之前呃正評嘅post<br />\n就係為左令啲起底嘅人睇到佢最近紀錄好多正評咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家起底睇佢6-12月嘅post就得<br />\n<br />\n傻狗<br />\n你半夜出五毛post<br />\n搵鬼睇咩<br />\n狗就係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無腦嘅"},{"pid":"52d518f561ea46a71005de7bcf4b5625144f2d12","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a298012ce704b35f0b01b09b0a20baa830ab24","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb19f234d81b53fc5705992c2289ad6de1caa02","tid":1866340,"uid":252492,"like":0,